Package ca.uqac.lif.cep.gnuplot

Processors for generating realtime graphs with the help of Gnuplot.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GnuplotCaller
    Processor taking as input a string containing a Gnuplot graph, and returning as its output the result of calling Gnuplot on that graph.
    GnuplotHeatMap
    Generates a Gnuplot file from a 2D Multiset.
    GnuplotProcessor
    Generic processor configuring basic parameters about the generation of a Gnuplot output string from an event trace.
    GnuplotScatterplot
    Generates a Gnuplot file from a 2D Multiset.
    PackageExtension
    Palette object for the processor included in this package.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GnuplotProcessor.Terminal
    The terminal used for the plot's output
